be adopted in the first place.

615
00:39:39,030 --> 00:39:40,239
Jay.

616
00:39:45,995 --> 00:39:47,121
What is this?

617
00:39:48,331 --> 00:39:51,417
Jay-jay still doesn't know the truth?

618
00:39:51,626 --> 00:39:52,919
Aries?

619
00:39:52,919 --> 00:39:55,504
You still haven't told Jay-jay
that you're siblings?

620
00:39:57,757 --> 00:40:00,343
Jay-jay, you still don't know
that Aries is your brother?

621
00:40:04,096 --> 00:40:05,473
Unbelievable!

622
00:40:16,734 --> 00:40:18,277
Now you know,

623
00:40:20,696 --> 00:40:22,365
but nothing will change between us.

624
00:40:26,327 --> 00:40:27,370
I know.

625
00:40:29,288 --> 00:40:31,832
You didn't even want me as a cousin,
how much more as a sibling.

626
00:40:45,721 --> 00:40:49,308
<i>What else can I do with </i>
<i>this soap-opera-like life of mine?</i>

627
00:41:22,758 --> 00:41:25,970
<i>Just keep going, Jay. </i>
<i>You can do this.</i>

628
00:41:41,819 --> 00:41:43,863
That's fine.

629
00:42:07,428 --> 00:42:08,888
What is this, a race?

630
00:42:10,973 --> 00:42:12,600
Is there a race going on here?

631
00:42:13,350 --> 00:42:14,435
Run!

632
00:42:15,102 --> 00:42:16,854
Holy shit!

633
00:42:17,521 --> 00:42:18,606
Run!

634
00:42:18,606 --> 00:42:20,357
What the fuck?!

635
00:42:26,030 --> 00:42:28,491
I'll report you to the police!

636
00:42:29,325 --> 00:42:30,284
You better run!

637
00:42:30,284 --> 00:42:31,285
Run!

638
00:42:36,665 --> 00:42:38,876
Shit.

639
00:42:43,506 --> 00:42:44,882
Stop it, wait!

640
00:42:45,966 --> 00:42:47,343
Damn it!

641
