Miss!

642
00:42:57,603 --> 00:42:58,521
Are you okay?

643
00:42:58,521 --> 00:42:59,522
Do you know those people?

644
00:42:59,522 --> 00:43:02,191
- I'm okay, I can manage.
- Miss, are you hurt?

645
00:43:02,441 --> 00:43:03,609
We'll take you to the hospital.

646
00:43:04,318 --> 00:43:05,361
No need.

647
00:43:05,361 --> 00:43:06,695
I still have to go to school.

648
00:43:06,695 --> 00:43:07,350
But you're hurt.

649
00:43:07,374 --> 00:43:09,365
You really don't want us
to take you to the hospital?

650
00:43:09,365 --> 00:43:10,533
I'm fine.

651
00:43:10,533 --> 00:43:11,700
It's okay.

652
00:43:12,368 --> 00:43:14,328
- Are you sure you can handle it?
- We'll take you home instead.

653
00:43:14,578 --> 00:43:16,455
I'm fine, thank you.

654
00:43:17,414 --> 00:43:19,375
- Alright, take care.
- Yes.

655
00:43:19,375 --> 00:43:20,793
You have bruises.

656
00:43:21,168 --> 00:43:24,088
- That poor child.
- I know.

657
00:43:25,131 --> 00:43:28,050
Who could those crazy people be?

658
00:43:28,050 --> 00:43:29,510
They're crazy.

659
00:43:38,978 --> 00:43:41,224
Keifer, there’s so much blood already!

660
00:43:41,480 --> 00:43:43,315
- That's enough!
- Keifer!

661
00:43:43,315 --> 00:43:45,109
- Kit didn’t do anything!
- Keifer!

662
00:43:45,109 --> 00:43:47,361
- Keifer, stop it.
- Keifer, have mercy on Kit.

663
00:43:48,154 --> 00:43:50,281
What is wrong with you?!
Are you going to kill Kit?!

664
00:43:50,906 --> 00:43:52,116
Hey!

665
00:43:52,366 --> 00:43:54,410
- Stop it already!
- Let go!

666
00:43:54,451 --> 00:43:56,328
What's your problem?!

667
00:43:57,329 --> 00:43:58,747
Huh?!

668
00:44:02,501 --> 00:44:04,044
Did he really kiss you?

669
00:44:04,336 --> 00:44:05,379
What?

670
00:44:05,754 --> 00:44:06,881
No!

671
00:44:08,507 --> 00:44:09,633
Mayo!

672
00:44:10,718 --> 00:44:14,513
Repeat what you asked Kit earlier.

673
00:44:14,972 --> 00:44:16,849
Did he really kiss Jay-jay?

674
00:44:19,852 --> 00:44:23,397
I asked Kit if he
liked Jay-jay because

675
00:44:27,026 --> 00:44:28,692
he tried to kiss her.

676
00:44:32,323 --> 00:44:35,075
If they hadn't fought,
I wouldn't have found out.

677
00:44:36,869 --> 00:44:38,412
Answer me, damn it!

678
00:44:38,412 --> 00:44:39,788
Keifer, calm down!

679
00:44:39,788 --> 00:44:41,763
Oh my God.

680
00:44:42,708 --> 00:44:44,335
Who else?!

681
00:44:45,377 --> 00:44:46,562
Huh?!

682
00:44:46,587 --> 00:44:48,631
Who fucking else?!

683
00:44:58,766 --> 00:45:00,184
Alright!

684
00:45:00,893 --> 00:45:03,938
Let's all find out together, shall we?

685
00:45:04,104 --> 00:45:05,981
Because maybe it turns
out we're not the only ones

686
00:45:05,981 --> 00:45:08,025
Jay has been playing with!

687
00:45:13,656 --> 00:45:14,657
You.

688
00:45:17,201 --> 00:45:21,372
Are you also in a
relationship with Jay-jay?

689
00:45:21,830 --> 00:45:22,831
No.

690
00:45:37,212 --> 00:45:38,213
You.

691
00:45:39,452 --> 00:45:41,329
Is it really Mica?

692
00:45:41,767 --> 00:45:44,228
Or do you also like Jay-jay?

693
00:45:47,106 --> 00:45:49,566
Keif, it's... it's just Mica.

694
00:45:54,530 --> 00:45:55,716
Of course.

695
00:45:57,658 --> 00:45:58,993
You.

696
00:46:08,168 --> 00:46:09,920
That's what you do, isn't it?

697
00:46:10,421 --> 00:46:12,047
Taking what's mine.

698
00:46:13,048 --> 00:46:14,677
First, Freya.

699
00:46:15,092 --> 00:46:16,583
Then, Ella.

700
00:46:16,927 --> 00:46:19,930
- And now, Jay-jay.
- Stop it!

701
00:46:19,972 --> 00:46:21,432
I didn't take anything from you!

702
00:46:21,432 --> 00:46:24,356
They were all with you
when I wanted to be with them!

703
00:46:24,977 --> 00:46:26,520
- Jay.
- Jay-jay.

704
00:46:27,229 --> 00:46:28,564
Are you okay?

705
00:46:28,564 --> 00:46:29,815
Come on, stand up.

706
00:46:34,987 --> 00:46:36,489
Is that what you want?

707
00:46:37,906 --> 00:46:40,450
The entire Section E flirting with you?

708
00:46:46,790 --> 00:46:49,060
Don't talk to me like that.

709
00:46:50,461 --> 00:46:53,547
Talk to me properly and
don't disrespect me.

710
00:46:55,514 --> 00:46:56,807
You feel disrespected?

711
00:47:00,137 --> 00:47:01,930
What about what you did to me?

712
00:47:02,681 --> 00:47:04,475
Isn't that disrespectful too?

713
00:47:10,773 --> 00:47:15,361
Or maybe you plan on
flirting with the entire Section E

714
00:47:15,361 --> 00:47:16,880
just to ruin us.

715
00:47:20,032 --> 00:47:21,278
Keifer!

716
00:47:27,748 --> 00:47:29,083
They're my friends.

717
00:47:29,083 --> 00:47:30,751
I'm Section E, too!

718
00:47:30,876 --> 00:47:32,628
Oh no, you're not.

719
00:47:35,923 --> 00:47:37,216
Keifer, where are you taking Jay-jay?

720
00:47:37,216 --> 00:47:38,942
Keifer, please have mercy!

721
00:47:38,967 --> 00:47:42,221
- We've got her.
- We got this.

722
00:47:42,763 --> 00:47:43,802
David.

723
00:47:45,599 --> 00:47:46,622
Shit!

724
00:47:51,313 --> 00:47:52,439
Keifer, stop it!

725
00:47:52,439 --> 00:47:54,274
Please! Keifer.

726
00:47:54,441 --> 00:47:55,901
Keifer, stop!

727
00:47:55,901 --> 00:47:57,694
Stay out of this.

728
00:48:04,993 --> 00:48:06,560
You don't belong in Section E.

729
00:48:06,703 --> 00:48:10,833
You belong to your stupid,
fucking, asshole cousin.

730
00:48:10,916 --> 00:48:13,043
What the hell are you doing here, Keifer?

731
00:48:13,210 --> 00:48:14,962
I'm returning her to you.

732
00:48:14,962 --> 00:48:17,214
She doesn't belong in Section E.

733
00:48:19,007 --> 00:48:20,509
Even more so here!

734
00:48:20,884 --> 00:48:22,219
That’s exactly why she
ended up in Section E,

735
00:48:22,219 --> 00:48:24,363
because all of you are equally useless.

736
00:48:24,388 --> 00:48:25,681
<i>That’s my brother?</i>

737
00:48:26,765 --> 00:48:28,475
<i>What exactly were you expecting, Jay?</i>

738
00:48:28,550 --> 00:48:30,510
Talking like you
don't care about her.

739
00:48:30,644 --> 00:48:31,895
I really don't.

740
00:48:33,480 --> 00:48:34,606
How about you?

741
00:48:34,606 --> 00:48:36,066
Weren't you her knight in shining armor?

742
00:48:36,066 --> 00:48:37,286
What happened?

743
00:48:37,401 --> 00:48:38,694
Stop it, Aries.

744
00:48:40,946 --> 00:48:44,241
Even if you drag her into your chaos,

745
00:48:44,241 --> 00:48:45,284
or drag her down into the dumps,

746
00:48:45,826 --> 00:48:47,035
I don't care.

747
00:48:47,035 --> 00:48:48,662
I don't fucking care.

748
00:49:10,225 --> 00:49:11,278
Jay.

749
00:49:12,811 --> 00:49:13,812
Jay.

750
00:49:36,418 --> 00:49:38,170
<i>Can I not go to school anymore?</i>

751
00:49:42,674 --> 00:49:46,887
<i>The words that were thrown at me</i>
<i>hurt more than any punch ever did.</i>

752
00:50:00,651 --> 00:50:03,153
<i>What's happening to us, Keifer?</i>

753
00:50:13,830 --> 00:50:15,457
<i>How are you, Jay?</i>

754
00:50:15,749 --> 00:50:17,209
<i>Call me please. </i>

755
00:50:17,584 --> 00:50:19,670
<i>Jay, I'm sorry for what happened.</i>

756
00:50:20,128 --> 00:50:21,713
<i>Are you okay?</i>

757
00:50:23,382 --> 00:50:24,566
<i>Jay...</i>

758
00:50:32,266 --> 00:50:38,397
<i>I can't go to school today, Ci.</i>

759
00:50:38,397 --> 00:50:41,733
Jay, it's already noon.
Aren't you going to school?

760
00:50:42,317 --> 00:50:44,611
Jay, this room of yours is unbelievable!

761
00:50:44,611 --> 00:50:46,488
It's such a mess.

762
00:50:46,488 --> 00:50:47,823
What are all these clothes?

763
00:50:47,823 --> 00:50:49,741
Are they clean or dirty?

764
00:50:49,741 --> 00:50:51,618
Why are they all mixed together?

765
00:50:51,618 --> 00:50:52,286
Goodness, Jay

766
00:50:52,286 --> 00:50:55,122
You shouldn't be messy with your room.

767
00:50:55,205 --> 00:50:57,124
You're a lady. What's this?

768
00:50:57,124 --> 00:50:59,126
Do you even use this for school?

769
00:50:59,293 --> 00:51:02,337
Oh my goodness!
Everything's a mess. Fix this, will you?

770
00:51:04,506 --> 00:51:05,591
Hey.

771
00:51:06,592 --> 00:51:07,801
Are you going to school?

772
00:51:08,343 --> 00:51:10,679
If not, just come with Andy and me.

773
00:51:10,679 --> 00:51:11,691
We're leaving.

774
00:51:12,617 --> 00:51:13,782
I'm going to school!

775
00:51:13,807 --> 00:51:15,033
Ouch!

776
00:51:15,058 --> 00:51:16,136
I'm going to school.

777
00:51:26,612 --> 00:51:28,155
- Stop it.
- Damn, what?!

778
00:51:28,155 --> 00:51:30,324
- Jay-jay might hear us.
- You don't have the guts, do you?

779
00:51:30,449 --> 00:51:31,783
Just tell her the truth already!

780
00:51:31,783 --> 00:51:33,660
- Hey!
- Don't boss Keifer around.

781
00:51:33,660 --> 00:51:35,120
- He'll say it eventually.
- Poor Jay-jay.

782
00:51:35,120 --> 00:51:36,622
He just needs time.

783
00:51:36,872 --> 00:51:38,373
I really feel sorry for Jay-jay.

784
00:51:39,124 --> 00:51:41,460
I told you to drop that plan!

785
00:51:41,460 --> 00:51:44,796
Don't play dumb. You were in
on that fucking plan!

786
00:51:44,911 --> 00:51:46,412
Just talk to her properly,

787
00:51:46,506 --> 00:51:48,175
then apologize to her.

788
00:51:48,175 --> 00:51:50,302
You really think it's that easy?

789
00:51:50,327 --> 00:51:52,454
Jay-jay will never forgive us anymore.

790
00:51:54,556 --> 00:51:56,683
- Jay.
- Jay.

791
00:51:56,850 --> 00:51:57,855
Oh.

792
00:51:58,051 --> 00:51:59,469
I thought you weren't coming to school?

793
00:52:01,229 --> 00:52:02,269
Jay.

794
00:52:04,608 --> 00:52:05,817
What plan?

795
00:52:07,582 --> 00:52:09,292
What plan are you talking about?

796
00:52:12,449 --> 00:52:13,511
Keifer.

797
00:52:13,992 --> 00:52:15,702
Just say it already.

798
00:52:21,375 --> 00:52:22,793
Fuck you, after
what happened yesterday,

799
00:52:22,793 --> 00:52:24,670
do you really think
you can still hurt me?

800
00:52:27,964 --> 00:52:29,174
Just say it.

801
00:52:37,557 --> 00:52:38,892
You sure you wanna hear it?

802
00:52:59,705 --> 00:53:01,248
I used you.

803
00:53:01,957 --> 00:53:05,050
And the whole Section E knows.

804
00:53:43,331 --> 00:53:45,621
I made you fall in love with me,

805
00:53:45,679 --> 00:53:47,681
just to get back at Aries.

806
00:54:00,731 --> 00:54:02,733
It was all part of my revenge.

807
00:54:06,855 --> 00:54:12,736
And everybody in Section E knew.

808
00:54:39,471 --> 00:54:42,058
So none of it was real?

809
00:54:43,058 --> 00:54:45,129
Everything you showed me?

810
00:54:49,648 --> 00:54:51,527
It was just part of my revenge.

811
00:55:41,366 --> 00:55:44,911
<i>I once said, there was no one else</i>
<i>who could hurt me anymore.</i>

812
00:55:45,954 --> 00:55:47,664
<i>But apparently, there still was.</i>

813
00:55:54,963 --> 00:55:55,505
Jay!

814
00:55:55,505 --> 00:55:57,632
<i>The person who I thought</i>
<i>would protect me.</i>

815
00:55:57,632 --> 00:55:58,698
Keifer.

816
00:55:59,384 --> 00:56:00,594
No.

817
00:56:01,595 --> 00:56:02,762
Don't cry.

818
00:56:04,187 --> 00:56:06,214
<i>The one who became my safe space.</i>

819
00:56:08,685 --> 00:56:10,854
I don't care about anything else,

820
00:56:10,854 --> 00:56:12,647
don't let me lose you too.

821
00:56:13,189 --> 00:56:14,566
I love you, Jay.

822
00:56:15,984 --> 00:56:17,903
I love you too, Keifer.

823
00:56:22,714 --> 00:56:24,917
<i>The person who I believed loved me...</i>

824
00:56:51,242 --> 00:56:53,034
<i>wasn't real after all.</i>

